# ─── Repo-specific data ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ship the compiled per-case SQLite bank (data/case_bank/) and the eval plots
# (assets/) — they are part of the submission. Ignore the raw CMS CSVs,
# the standalone research notebooks, and any local-only docs.

# Raw public-domain CMS CSVs are huge (multi-GB) — never commit them.
/data/All Beneficiary Years/
/data/All FFS Claims/
/data/pde.csv
/data/raw/
/data/*.csv

# Generated multi-modal evidence inside per-case dirs is heavy — ignore by glob.
# The medicare_records.db files (the actual training signal) ARE committed.
data/case_bank/**/scanned_claims/
data/case_bank/**/intercepted_comms/

# Internal hackathon scratch (kept off GitHub / HF Space)
/dataset_ideas/
/hackathon_docs/
/docs/
/.claude/
CLAUDE.md
research_and_eda.ipynb

